man(1) iTMSTransporter - iTunes Store Transporter man(1)

NAME

iTMSTransporter - deliver content to iTunes, the App Store, and Apple Books.

SYNOPSIS

iTMSTransporter [-help <mode> | -info | -m <mode> | -version]

DESCRIPTION

See the user's guide at: https://help.apple.com/itc/transporteruserguide

OPTIONS

-help <mode>
Requests the help for the specified <mode>. If <mode> is not specified, general help is displayed.
-info
Displays the copyright notice and acknowledgements.
-m <mode>
Runs iTMSTransporter in <mode>, see user's guide for more details.
-version
Displays the version information.

SEE ALSO

altool(1)
